    <div class="container">
        <p style="color:  #167cd0;padding: 1em;text-align: left;">
            In the pandemic, local businesses have been hit the hardest by the lack of in-person shoppers. Many of my friends and I would love to support more local businesses but we are limited to shops near us, and of those many have closed down due to the lack
            of customers, and we resort to mainstream grocers. By making more people aware of local businesses that deliver, not only do we support the business, but we also support vulnerable people by leaving the limited delivery slots of mainstream
            supermarkets open to those who need it. Additionally, many of these companies are environmentally aware or ethical about how they source their products. I hope you find a company that fits your needs and support them. Thank you!

        </p>
